when I was little, you know?

02:26.513 --> 02:30.522
Hit man, the secret agent man, you know.

02:33.104 --> 02:35.071
Two things I always wanted...

02:35.171 --> 02:37.911
wanted to do, but...

02:38.448 --> 02:42.937
