37:18.381 --> 37:20.525
Is that your wife?

37:26.734 --> 37:28.688
Beautiful woman.

37:30.606 --> 37:32.662
Who are you with?

37:32.966 --> 37:35.608
No one. Just me.

37:37.454 --> 37:39.644
Then how did you get in?

37:41.070 --> 37:44.339
A woman can achieve
anything she desires.

37:44.910 --> 37:47.306
Not everything is attainable.

37:47.406 --> 37:49.404
Maybe for some.

37:50.350 --> 37:53.812
This woman can get everything she wants.

38:29.998 --> 38:32.684
Fucking do not even play.

38:33.288 --> 38:35.359
What the fuck?

38:36.499 --> 38:39.676
I'm so sorry. I'll clean it up.

38:40.014 --> 38:41.519
I'm sorry.

38:41.806 --> 38:44.074
Is this Yves Saint Laurent?

38:44.174 --> 38:47.325
I love a handsome man with good taste.

38:50.354 --> 38:55.754
I'm sorry. I shouldn't speak my mind
in front of your girlfriend?

38:55.854 --> 38:58.347
Some things are better left unsaid?

38:58.447 --> 39:00.157
Girlfriend?

39:00.463 --> 39:03.505
Oh, no, no, I barely know this bitch.

39:04.270 --> 39:06.397
Fucking asshole.

39:09.390 --> 39:12.971
- May I buy you a drink?
- Oh, I think you may.

39:13.071 --> 39:16.229
- Well, what's your weapon of choice?
- What?

39:16.590 --> 39:19.353
Sorry, I guess that's an American thing.

39:19.453 --> 39:22.220
What kind of drink do you like?

39:23.183 --> 39:25.213
I'm sorry.

39:25.518 --> 39:28.796
I'm having whatever you're having.

39:29.390 --> 39:31.691
- Is that okay?
- That's a good choice, baby.

39:31.791 --> 39:35.407
Oh, baby again. I love you Americans.

39:35.599 --> 39:38.398
- One more.
- Thank you.

39:39.341 --> 39:43.978
I need to go to the restroom.
You're not going to leave me, are you?

39:44.078 --> 39:45.757
No.

39:51.343 --> 39:53.931
Nice piece of ass right there, bro.
You're the fucking man.

39:54.031 --> 39:56.316
Damn right, I'm the fucking man.

39:57.134 --> 39:59.557
That'll be 30 bucks, fellas.

40:04.750 --> 40:07.019
- My fucking wallet, dude.
- Dude, you just had it.

40:07.119 --> 40:09.135
I know I just had it, it's fucking gone.

40:09.602 --> 40:13.198
- The fucking Russian bitch stole your wallet.
- No fucking way, dude.

40:13.773 --> 40:16.467
Pretty fucking bitch took my wallet.

40:40.207 --> 40:43.004
Nice job on the quick turnaround.

40:43.790 --> 40:45.981
You got it, baby.

40:46.670 --> 40:50.218
I've got a Asian customer
been dying for this one.

40:50.318 --> 40:53.212
He's a cheap motherfucker, though.

40:53.646 --> 40:55.309
Relax.

40:55.409 --> 40:57.692
I always take care of you,

40:57.792 --> 40:59.493
don't I?

41:01.198 --> 41:03.593
Somebody left this for you.

41:03.693 --> 41:07.081
- Who gave this to you?
- Some kid dropped it off.

41:07.181 --> 41:11.273
By the way,
this ain't a fucking post office.

41:11.373 --> 41:15.150
I don't know you, and you don't know me.

41:15.438 --> 41:17.180
Get it?

42:05.358 --> 42:09.007
Hello, Olivia.
Get in, let's have a chat.

42:09.966 --> 42:12.592
Who are you? How do you know me?

42:13.550 --> 42:18.154
I got a score for you.
Get in, and I'll give you the details.

42:18.254 --> 42:19.962
How do you know I'm not wired?

42:20.845 --> 42:24.797
Because a million dollar score
is worth more than a wire to a cop.

42:25.805 --> 42:27.773
Now, you get in, or I fuck off.

42:43.629 --> 42:45.949
I've never heard of a no-split deal.

42:46.574 --> 42:48.509
What's your game?

42:49.549 --> 42:52.810
I get what I want,
you get what you want.

42:52.910 --> 42:54.826
What is that you want?

42:54.926 --> 42:58.826
Sonny "Sundown" Garcia.
You ever heard of him?

42:58.926 --> 43:00.526
Nope.

43:00.813 --> 43:03.978
Well, he's got something
that should've been mine.

43:04.078 --> 43:06.396
I want you to get it for me.

43:06.510 --> 43:08.586
What's the score?

43:08.686 --> 43:10.652
A necklace.

43:12.014 --> 43:13.902
The million dollar necklace?

43:14.574 --> 43:16.253
Yeah.

43:16.814 --> 43:19.587
How much is worth a man's freedom.

44:20.014 --> 44:21.825
<i>Vámanos.</i>

44:41.134 --> 44:42.491
<i>It means the world to him.</i>

44:43.214 --> 44:44.654
I need you to rid him of it.

44:44.942 --> 44:46.460
So...

44:46.560 --> 44:52.284
just to make sure, you want me to take
that necklace and walk away?

44:52.718 --> 44:54.588
No split.

44:54.894 --> 44:57.546
- No split.
- Why?

44:57.646 --> 45:00.512
Because he bought that chain in blood.

45:06.254 --> 45:08.593
<i>The bosses have a lot of pull in Mexico.</i>

45:08.693 --> 45:11.626
<i>It was too easy for them
to pin her murder on me.</i>

45:11.726 --> 45:15.068
<i>One phone call, and a small payoff
to some corrupt cops.</i>

45:21.294 --> 45:23.421
<i>Call it a day.</i>

45:26.350 --> 45:31.580
<i>For his so-called loyalty, the boss ensured
that I got the worst treatment imaginable.</i>

45:36.430 --> 45:40.169
<i>Twenty years, twenty hard years
those motherfuckers gave me</i>

45:40.269 --> 45:42.250
<i>for a crime I did not commit.</i>

45:42.350 --> 45:47.164
<i>And worst of all, for murdering the woman
I would've given my life for.</i>

45:47.726 --> 45:49.738
<i>Those are wounds that will never heal.</i>

45:49.838 --> 45:54.454
<i>All for a chain
and the fucking bullshit it represents.</i>

45:54.554 --> 45:59.498
<i>That chain is meant to buy him
his freedom if the need ever arises.</i>

45:59.598 --> 46:00.586
<i>And it cost me mine.</i>

46:00.686 --> 46:05.340
<i>Before I have him killed, I need you
to take that chain away from him.</i>

46:06.349 --> 46:09.010
<i>$500,000 if I split it.</i>

46:11.053 --> 46:12.906
Consider it done.

46:13.006 --> 46:15.694
- I said a million.
- Black market.

46:16.078 --> 46:18.030
Smart girl.

46:18.318 --> 46:21.022
There is one more thing you should know.

46:21.742 --> 46:24.542
He's got a soft spot for pretty girls.

46:27.725 --> 46:29.948
That's why you picked me.

47:12.174 --> 47:14.293
Who sent you?

47:17.101 --> 47:18.652
What do you mean?

47:27.917 --> 47:30.780
I haven't been this lucky
in a long time.

47:37.294 --> 47:40.107
Oh, fuck.

47:42.541 --> 47:44.093
Yeah?

47:47.213 --> 47:49.194
I'll be right there.

47:49.294 --> 47:51.402
I gotta go. Gotta work.

47:51.502 --> 47:55.563
Hey, hey, hey, hey. Five more minutes.

47:55.663 --> 47:58.621
I'll make it worth your while.

48:07.373 --> 48:09.340
I wish I could.

48:12.877 --> 48:14.933
I gotta go.

48:23.022 --> 48:25.148
I'll be in touch.

48:48.366 --> 48:52.157
Holy crap, man.
You scared the shit out of me.

48:53.582 --> 48:56.206
- Did you find her?
- Jeez, man.

48:56.589 --> 48:59.100
Don't creep up on people like that.

48:59.534 --> 49:02.953
Yes, I found her. It's not good news.

49:03.053 --> 49:05.820
What do you mean, "it's not good news"?
Is she dead?

49:07.341 --> 49:09.127
Far from it.

49:09.227 --> 49:12.202
This is her in Monaco
outside the Ritz-Carlton.

49:12.302 --> 49:15.574
